  <developerConceptualDocument xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <introduction>
      <para>Error BE0013: Possible invalid path '<localUri>[path]</localUri>'</para>
    </introduction>

    <section>
      <title>Cause</title>
      <content>
        <para>This is caused by a potentially invalid path on a
<codeInline>source</codeInline> attribute on a <codeInline>code</codeInline>
element in an HTML additional content file.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Solution</title>
      <content>
        <para>The file in which the error occurred will be listed just above
the error message in the log file.  Load it and search for <codeInline>code</codeInline>
elements that import source code from external files.  Check the paths to
ensure that they are correct and valid.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

